nodes.title: Unnamed
widgets_values:
Everything in this workflow is setup to utilize rgthree's context nodes in order to mute nodes.

When you mute a node it ceases to function. Nothing goes in and nothing comes out. 

The benefit of this vs bypassing is that they no longer consume resources. 

Where-as bypassing still has to go through those which is using resources and slowing everything down.
